import { createRoot } from "react-dom/client";

import "./styles.css";

const root = createRoot(document.querySelector("#root"));

root.render(
  <>
    <group>
      <mesh>
        <boxGeometry />
        <meshBasicMaterial color='blue' />
      </mesh>
      <mesh>
        <boxGeometry />
        <meshBasicMaterial color='red' />
      </mesh>
    </group>
  </>
);
